description: Disturbing video shows a pro-Palestine protester knocked out cold in the streets of New York as demonstrators sweep through the city.

description: Scandal-plagued Fulton County District Attorney Fani Willis could already be kicked off the case for her relationship with a lawyer she hired to help run it. Now she could lose her job entirely.
